item.title: "Choose Life" They say.
item.description: “Choose Life” They say. Choose Life. Choose a job. Choose a career. Choose a family. Choose fixed interest mortgage repayments. Choose a starter home. Choose your friends. Choose leisurewear and matching luggage. Choose a three-piece suit on hire purchase in a range of fucking fabrics.
